00:34:25,455 --> 00:34:28,375
because Shin Ha-ri, or Shin Na-ri,
or whatever her name is,

595
00:34:28,458 --> 00:34:31,211
didn't bother to catch an old man
as he was falling over?

596
00:34:31,294 --> 00:34:35,716
