716
00:43:10,008 --> 00:43:11,134
I like it too.

717
00:43:11,801 --> 00:43:16,014
You have an excellent eye, sir.
Let me help you with your payment.

718
00:43:18,683 --> 00:43:21,269
Do you have a bigger size?
I can't zip this up.

719
00:43:21,353 --> 00:43:23,730
