725
00:43:48,129 --> 00:43:52,217
Hello. Long time, no see.

726
00:43:52,300 --> 00:43:53,218
Oh, my god!

727
00:43:53,301 --> 00:43:56,096
Ms. Jo! It's been so long
since we last saw you!

728
00:43:56,179 --> 00:43:59,724
