749
00:45:06,124 --> 00:45:09,252
Hello, my babies.

750
00:45:09,335 --> 00:45:11,462
Okay.

751
00:45:12,380 --> 00:45:14,424
Ms. Jin.

752
00:45:15,425 --> 00:45:16,593
What are you doing?

753
00:45:16,673 --> 00:45:21,261
-Aren't you going to greet your director?
